biography: Kelly Porter is known for her work on Full Ride (2023), Haul out the Holly (2022), The Holiday Stocking (2022), Pleasant Grove (2021), Trespassers (2022), Power Rangers: Origins, All We need for Christmas (2021), Love in the Limelight (2022), and The Gabby Petito Story. Kelly is a licensed cosmetologist and barber in the state of Utah. She is a certified makeup artist, and basic esthetician.
name: Kelly Porter
